data.description: This BEAUTIFUL Pulte home offers breathtaking GREENBELT views along Lake Lavon! Located in the award-winning community of Inspiration, you have full access to 5 pools, LAZY RIVER, parks, 2 story fitness center, Club Inspiration, zip line, dog parks, pickleball, volleyball, and SO MUCH MORE! The spacious living area features an abundance of natural light and is open to the kitchen and dining area, as well as the tech center-office. The kitchen is a chef's delight, with granite countertops, ss appliances, ample cabinet space, pantry and large island w seating. The primary suite is a true retreat w large windows framing the picturesque greenery. It features a luxurious bathroom with double sinks, tub, and separate shower. Three additional bedrooms offer plenty of space for family and guests. All of this with easy-to-maintain tile flooring throughout! Relax on the covered patio, play in the large grassy yard, and enjoy the VIEWS! Massage chair INCLUDED! Fridge, washer and dryer STAY!
